72
00:05:18,699 --> 00:05:21,076
Dia tak membaca pesan
dan menjawab telepon.

73
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,412
Mungkin saja dia sedang ingin membolos.

74
00:05:23,495 --> 00:05:24,580
Na-bi itu bukan kau.

75
00:05:25,623 --> 00:05:27,374
Kami pergi. Sampai besok!

76
00:05:27,458 --> 00:05:28,709
- Kelasnya menyenangkan.
- Dah.

77
00:05:28,792 --> 00:05:30,669
