96
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,183
Apa maksudmu "lolos"?

97
00:07:50,726 --> 00:07:52,061
Bukan begitu.

98
00:07:53,771 --> 00:07:55,189
Aku putus dengan Chris.

99
00:07:56,315 --> 00:07:57,274
Kenapa?

100
00:08:00,736 --> 00:08:03,197
Seorang Park Jae-eon menanyakan alasannya?

101
00:08:05,491 --> 00:08:08,452
Kupikir dekat denganmu saat mengencaninya

102
00:08:08,952 --> 00:08:11,288
