103
00:08:12,748 --> 00:08:15,584
Kini, aku juga tahu rasanya.

104
00:08:16,418 --> 00:08:19,338
Jadi, kalian putus begitu saja?

105
00:08:19,421 --> 00:08:22,508
Ya. Aku melepaskannya tanpa penyelesaian.

106
00:08:23,884 --> 00:08:24,968
Aku hebat, 'kan?

107
00:08:28,597 --> 00:08:31,600
Kenapa? Itulah yang paling kau benci.

108
00:08:32,267 --> 00:08:34,186
