115
00:09:43,589 --> 00:09:45,299
<i>Dia menghilang.</i>

116
00:09:55,684 --> 00:09:57,227
Terima kasih!

117
00:09:57,853 --> 00:09:59,146
Yu Na-bi!

118
00:09:59,688 --> 00:10:00,981
Bibi!

119
00:10:03,734 --> 00:10:07,321
Astaga.

120
00:10:08,405 --> 00:10:10,365
Perjalanan panjang, ya?

121
00:10:12,701 --> 00:10:14,203
- Aku jadi teringat, Bi.
- Apa?

122
00:10:14,286 --> 00:10:16,914
