124
00:10:20,751 --> 00:10:22,669
Tidak seperti itu.

125
00:10:22,753 --> 00:10:24,254
Maka tak masalah.

126
00:10:25,005 --> 00:10:26,381
Berapa lama mau di sini?

127
00:10:26,465 --> 00:10:29,635
Sekitar satu minggu?

128
00:10:29,718 --> 00:10:31,762
Astaga, selama itu?

129
00:10:33,055 --> 00:10:35,891
Kenapa? Tak mau aku di sini?

130
00:10:35,974 --> 00:10:37,351
Bukan begitu.

131
00:10:39,311 --> 00:10:41,063
Aku akan merapikan rumahmu.

132
00:10:41,146 --> 00:10:44,066
Benar. Selagi perasaanmu kurang baik,

133
00:10:44,149 --> 00:10:46,652
kau bisa membereskan pekerjaan rumah.

134
00:10:46,735 --> 00:10:48,987
Tentu, akan kulakukan.

135
00:10:59,873 --> 00:11:01,917
STUDIO TEMBIKAR

136
00:11:05,587 --> 00:11:07,130
Menyegarkan.

137
00:11:07,214 --> 00:11:10,050
- Cuacanya indah.
- Indah sekali.

138
00:11:10,133 --> 00:11:12,928
